ActProceeds of Crime (Money Laundering) and Terrorist Financing Act
PrecisEnactment of the CROSS-BORDER CURRENCY AND MONETARY INSTRUMENTS REPORTING REGULATIONS which oblige those who import or export currency or other monetary instruments valued at $10,000 or more to submit a written report to a customs officer at the border-crossing point or at the nearest customs office that is open for business.
